    "name": "cdr_type",
    "label": "CDR type",
    "help": "<p>The <strong>CDR</strong> covers the period October 2002 to March 2015 for version 1.0, and October 2002 to April 2020 for version 2.0.</p> <p>The <strong>ICDR</strong> covers the period from April 2015 onward for version 1.0, and October 2020 onward for version 2.0.</p> <p>Note that the quality and accuracy of the data record are higher during the CryoSat-2 period than during the Envisat period. As a result, care should be taken when combining the two missions to assess long-term changes and trends.</p>",
